<section class="py-16 px-6 border-[3px] border-red-200">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h3 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-8 warning-text">THE MISTAKE</h3>
    
    <div class="bg-red-50 border-[3px] warning-border p-8 mb-12">
      <h4 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4">üí¨ WHAT HAPPENED</h4>
      <p class="text-lg">
        <strong>Two years ago, I needed a website for my consulting business.</strong> Saw an ad for an AI builder (let's call it "Builder X"), loved the "generate in 30 seconds" pitch. Signed up for annual plan ($312/year). Built site in an hour, launched same day. Thought I was genius for being so efficient. <span class="font-bold">Six months later, business grew. Needed blog for SEO, wanted e-commerce to sell digital products, needed more customization than Builder X allowed. Wanted to leave. Discovered Builder X doesn't allow code export. Trapped. Had to rebuild entire site from scratch on new platform. Total cost: $12,000 (developer fees + lost time + opportunity cost). Here's what I learned the hard way.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border-[3px] border-red-500">
